               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipits and headings of the texts; directives for the ministers; the word "ʾǝgäle" in supplication formulas; abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs and Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
On the incipit page of Texts I and III-3 (fols. 4r, 82r), few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</rubric>
